title: New revelations raise fresh questions about Trump's past ties to sex offender Epstein
subhed: Democrats have released several emails from the financier, who died by suicide in prison in 2019. In one, he expressed satisfaction with the current US president's silence and stated that a victim 'spent hours' at his home in Trump's company. In another, he claimed that the president 'of course knew about the girls since he asked Ghislaine to stop.'
